 Tested Devices
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Currently only Panasonic DMR devices have been tested. If you successfully
 recovered the content of your drive (completly or partly), please drop me a
 mail!

 Working devices:

  * Panasonic DMR-EH55
  * Panasonic DMR-EH56
  * Panasonic DMR-EH57



 System Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 To run the script you need a Python interpreter (2.x, tested with 2.5 and
 higher).



